_sText:
Another one of my map releases for a long time. I didn't intend it to be like iceworld, but it did. The idea's came as I was making it. It's a small, but hopefully fun map. It's iceworld advanced, but everything is transparent.


aim_iceworld_advanced

To install, copy the 'cstrike' folder to your counter-strike source folder found in

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\<USERNAME>\counter-strike source\

and you're ready to play.


Map created by ToySoldiers
